class User {
  + externalAuthProvider (Google/Microsoft/Facebook)
  + externalUserId
  + displayName
  + email
}

class Role {
  + Can be:
  + Port Authority Officer
  + Shipping Agent Representative
  + Logistics Operator
  + Administrator

}

note right of Role
  Port Authority Officer:
    - Review and approve/reject VesselVisit notifications
    - Review and approve/reject ShippingAgentOrgRequest
    - Assign docks to approved visits
    - Monitor port operations for compliance
  
  Shipping Agent Representative:
    - Submit VesselVisit notifications
    - Provide cargo manifests
    - Update/cancel notifications before approval
    - Monitor status of visits
  
  Logistics Operator:
    - Define and schedule operational tasks for approved visits
    - Allocate resources (cranes, trucks, yard equipment, staff)
    - Monitor task execution
    - Handle operational adjustments
  
  Administrator:
    - Manage user accounts and permissions
    - Configure system parameters
    - Maintain operational data integrity
end note

